## WebSocket Services

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant WS as Socket.io
    participant CtxWS as ContextWS
    participant Pipeline as ParallelContextPipeline
    participant Cache as ContextCache

    Client->>WS: connect(token)
    WS->>CtxWS: authenticate(token)
    CtxWS->>WS: authenticated
    
    Client->>WS: start_context_assembly(params)
    WS->>CtxWS: handle_start_assembly(params)
    
    CtxWS->>Pipeline: assembleStreaming(params)
    
    Note over Pipeline: Yields chunks
    
    loop Streaming
        Pipeline->>CtxWS: chunk{priority, content}
        CtxWS->>Client: context_chunk
    end
    
    Client->>WS: update_context(query)
    WS->>CtxWS: handle_update
    CtxWS->>Cache: invalidate(query)
    CtxWS->>Pipeline: partial_retrieve(query)
    Pipeline->>CtxWS: partial_context
    CtxWS->>Client: context_update

    Client->>WS: disconnect
    WS->>CtxWS: handle_disconnect
    CtxWS->>Cache: release_resources
```

