## Error Handling & Circuit Breaker

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    subgraph "Circuit Breaker Service"
        
        cb_init["CircuitBreaker class"]
        states["States: CLOSED, OPEN, HALF_OPEN"]
        
        subgraph "Closed State"
            normal["Normal operation"]
            count_fail["Count failures"]
            threshold["failureThreshold reached?"]
        end

        subgraph "Open State"
            reject["Reject requests"]
            timer["Wait timeout"]
            timeout["Timeout reached?"]
        end

        subgraph "Half-Open State"
            probe["Probe request"]
            success["Success?"]
            close["Close circuit"]
            open["Re-open circuit"]
        end
    end

    subgraph "Error Types"
        err_auth["AuthError - 401"]
        err_perm["PermissionError - 403"]
        err_notfound["NotFoundError - 404"]
        err_validation["ValidationError - 400"]
        err_rate["RateLimitError - 429"]
        err_server["ServerError - 500"]
    end

    normal --> count_fail
    count_fail --> threshold
    threshold -->|Yes| reject
    reject --> timer
    timer --> timeout
    timeout -->|Yes| probe
    
    probe --> success
    success -->|Yes| close
    success -->|No| open

    style cb_init fill:#1a1a2e,stroke:#4a4a6a
    style err_server fill:#4a1942,stroke:#d4145a
```